is a dog and a scoundrel too!

201
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:28,000
It's so crowded here!

202
00:18:28,728 --> 00:18:32,760
I don't think our turn will ever come.
- Yes, looks like we've blown the money

203
00:18:34,166 --> 00:18:37,080
Want an admission guys...? I have
a setting with the manager himself

204
00:18:37,485 --> 00:18:39,880
I'll get it for you in a moment.
- He's trying to con us

205
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:42,720
We don't talk to
small fries, okay?

206
00:18:47,821 --> 00:18:51,291
