- What conmen!

207
00:18:51,371 --> 00:18:53,560
Crazy guy, don't look at him

208
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:56,920
That's fifty thousand. Count it.
- It's all right

209
00:18:58,784 --> 00:19:01,384
Bantu, there is something wrong

210
00:19:02,024 --> 00:19:05,504
Everything is wrong.
- What do you mean?

211
00:19:06,104 --> 00:19:08,424
Just that the manager of
this hotel is collecting 50,000

212
00:19:08,504 --> 00:19:11,064
from everyone for an admission.

213
00:19:11,345 --> 00:19:14,624
