214
00:19:14,837 --> 00:19:18,864
Oh yes. Corruption is here
to stay in our country

215
00:19:19,664 --> 00:19:22,704
It's not happening. Let's go.
- Sit down!

216
00:19:22,912 --> 00:19:25,904
We'll use formula 36. The manager
will give us an admission...

217
00:19:25,984 --> 00:19:27,824
