01:16:44,505 --> 01:16:49,154
Chantu and Bantu! Their
names also are so middle class

956
01:16:49,327 --> 01:16:51,574
Daddy, no one cares for class here

957
01:16:52,014 --> 01:16:55,814
But dear, I will find
grooms for you...

958
01:16:55,974 --> 01:16:59,727
...who, even after being reprimanded
by you, will run our resort well.

959
01:16:59,997 --> 01:17:04,734
Daddy, you only praised
them to the hilt yesterday.

960
01:17:05,284 --> 01:17:10,645
Haven't you heard the phrase? One
has a different facet for the public.

961
01:17:11,402 --> 01:17:17,542
What we did yesterday was that.
- That was our public facet.

962
01:17:17,622 --> 01:17:22,602
All right, then get this clear.
We will elope and marry them.

963
01:17:22,755 --> 01:17:26,656
You will be disgraced.
- People will spit at you.

964
01:17:27,185 --> 01:17:29,715
You will lose face.

965
01:17:31,109 --> 01:17:34,155
Khurana, that's a
horrible picture she's showing.

966
01:17:34,915 --> 01:17:38,082
We'll have to take the help of that.
- Of goons?

967
01:17:39,833 --> 01:17:40,835
Brains.

968
01:17:41,271 --> 01:17:43,995
I have realized.

969
01:17:45,087 --> 01:17:48,114
Look dear, ask Chantu & Bantu
to come and meet us.

970
01:17:50,687 --> 01:17:53,292
We'll ask them
to come and meet you.

971
01:17:56,612 --> 01:18:00,027
What have you done?
- I'll tell you

972
01:18:01,378 --> 01:18:03,056
Just let them come to meet us

973
01:18:03,930 --> 01:18:06,239
I will play a trick which
will make them say...

974
01:18:06,319 --> 01:18:08,616
...they don't want to
marry our daughters.

975
01:18:08,696 --> 01:18:10,038
How is that?

976
01:18:14,946 --> 01:18:19,839
Wow! What a great that.
- Isn't it a great idea?

977
01:18:19,919 --> 01:18:26,131
Let Chantu and Bantu come.
And watch the fun!

978
01:18:27,162 --> 01:18:28,405
What happened?

979
01:18:30,185 --> 01:18:31,745
Nothing! Nothing at all!

980
01:18:32,405 --> 01:18:34,785
We have scrounged all the hotels
in Goa in the last 15 days

981
01:18:35,119 --> 01:18:37,625
Despite being gold medalists,
forget as a manager...

982
01:18:37,951 --> 01:18:39,705
no one is ready to
appoint us even as waiters

983
01:18:39,875 --> 01:18:43,305
They are all demanding bribes
of 25,000 and 50,000

984
01:18:43,788 --> 01:18:47,425
Only a local joint remains now,
should we try there?

985
01:18:47,505 --> 01:18:49,853
Don't joke. We don't even
have any money left now.

986
01:18:50,097 --> 01:18:53,377
We'll have to spend the night eating
grams, and return home tomorrow

987
01:18:53,577 --> 01:18:56,337
How can we go home like that?
How will we face Sundri and Mundri?

988
01:18:56,869 --> 01:19:01,204
We'll have to do something. Hey!
There is one financier in this city...

989
01:19:01,284 --> 01:19:04,617
who can give us some money.
- Who?

990
01:19:16,556 --> 01:19:22,604
Chantu! You scored excellent marks.
What more do you want in life?

991
01:19:22,771 --> 01:19:24,244
It's all by your grace.

992
01:19:25,684 --> 01:19:28,324
Sir, a sweet little girl
wants to meet you, sir

993
01:19:28,544 --> 01:19:32,684
Girl? She wants admission?
- I don't know

994
01:19:32,890 --> 01:19:34,484
Call her in.
- Yes sir

995
01:19:35,084 --> 01:19:36,084
Come in, sister

996
01:19:46,410 --> 01:19:49,323
What are you doing here?
- Where else can I go?

997
01:19:49,403 --> 01:19:54,250
Keep your hands away! What's this?
- A baby. A gift from you

998
01:19:54,650 --> 01:19:57,890
I gave you my purse, my chain,
not this

999
01:19:57,970 --> 01:19:59,730
Now you don't stare at me,
tell her!

1000
01:20:00,296 --> 01:20:03,650
How do I know, sir?
I entered after the climax

1001
01:20:03,770 --> 01:20:06,650
There was nothing in the movie
except the climax

1002
01:20:08,004 --> 01:20:10,450
I will stay here.
I won't go anywhere!

1003
01:20:10,770 --> 01:20:15,130
Sir, such women cannot be trusted

1004
01:20:15,210 --> 01:20:17,450
Pay her Rs.50-60 thousand
and send her away

1005
01:20:17,570 --> 01:20:21,250
All right. 50-60...?
- Pay her a lakh or two

1006
01:20:21,330 --> 01:20:24,250
A lakh or two! Get out of here!
Get out of my sight!

1007
01:20:24,330 --> 01:20:27,690
And you unchaste woman!
Just get out of my sight!

1008
01:20:28,650 --> 01:20:31,330
Then who will support this baby?

1009
01:20:36,739 --> 01:20:39,059
Such a big deception,
you cheap woman!

1010
01:20:40,579 --> 01:20:42,899
Let's go!
- Where are you going!

1011
01:20:44,219 --> 01:20:46,219
Bantu, you!
- Is my hair okay, sir?

1012
01:20:46,339 --> 01:20:48,819
I won't spare you two!
Where is my revolver?

1013
01:20:54,419 --> 01:20:58,339
I won't spare them!
I will take revenge!

1014
01:20:58,568 --> 01:21:02,547
What! Khanna and Khurana want
to meet us? To discuss marriage?

1015
01:21:02,787 --> 01:21:05,627
Yes. We have been looking for
you since the past four days

1016
01:21:05,907 --> 01:21:09,307
And you are eating bhelpuri over here.
- We've made it!

1017
01:21:09,387 --> 01:21:10,827
Yes.
- This is not the time to joke

1018
01:22:42,827 --> 01:22:45,187
Our whole future is
dependent on this meeting

1019
01:22:45,368 --> 01:22:48,267
Yes, she's right.
We'll know after this meeting...

1020
01:22:48,347 --> 01:22:50,867
whether we'll live in a
shanty or a mansion

1021
01:22:51,260 --> 01:22:52,987
Whether our children will study
in a good school and eat burgers...

1022
01:22:53,206 --> 01:22:54,787
or street snacks
outside a municipal school.

1023
01:22:55,703 --> 01:22:57,732
Is this meeting so serious?

1024
01:22:57,812 --> 01:23:00,412
Yes. We'll have to make
this meeting click so well...

1025
01:23:00,492 --> 01:23:01,892
that it sets our lives

1026
01:23:05,908 --> 01:23:07,396
What will your father ask?

1027
01:23:07,794 --> 01:23:12,342
What do you have which will make
us give you our daughters in marriage?

1028
01:23:12,700 --> 01:23:16,460
We have everything. Two legs, two
hands, two ears, two eyes, and one...

1029
01:23:16,540 --> 01:23:18,154
Enough!
- Nose, sir

1030
01:23:18,430 --> 01:23:21,470
Don't go further.
An ass has four of those

1031
01:23:21,838 --> 01:23:24,670
That doesn't mean we get
our daughters that with them

1032
01:23:24,750 --> 01:23:26,950
Get our daughters married to them.

1033
01:23:27,030 --> 01:23:31,206
When life shows that, even
the tough show that and run away

1034
01:23:31,286 --> 01:23:34,354
What do they show, sir?
- When life becomes a challenge...

1035
01:23:34,434 --> 01:23:36,914
even the tough show
their backs and run away

1036
01:23:37,104 --> 01:23:40,443
We are ready to
face any challenge, sir

1037
01:23:40,908 --> 01:23:42,468
Think again

1038
01:23:43,410 --> 01:23:45,508
Had he been thinking,
he'd not have had the brawn

1039
01:23:45,823 --> 01:23:48,388
But now that he has,
we accept the challenge

1040
01:23:49,481 --> 01:23:53,045
Shall I tell them? We have a that
that's of no use

1041
01:23:53,125 --> 01:23:56,668
What are you saying, sir!
- He's talking of our health resort

1042
01:23:57,299 --> 01:23:59,990
A local goon has shut it down

1043
01:24:00,266 --> 01:24:04,868
If you can restart that resort and
run it for at least a year...

1044
01:24:04,948 --> 01:24:08,508
...only then can we think of
accepting you as our sons-in-law.

1045
01:24:09,486 --> 01:24:12,980
Until then, you two will
not meet our daughters.

1046
01:24:17,604 --> 01:24:20,364
Look daddy, if you disapprove
of our marriage, just say so

1047
01:24:20,859 --> 01:24:24,284
At least don't conspire to get
our love killed by those goons

1048
01:24:24,364 --> 01:24:27,204
But they said they are
ready to accept any challenge.

1049
01:24:27,545 --> 01:24:30,524
Yes, but they didn't know
you will push them to their death

1050
01:24:30,604 --> 01:24:35,284
A challenge can be anything.
- The challenged must have that

1051
01:24:35,622 --> 01:24:36,686
Courage

1052
01:24:36,876 --> 01:24:41,295
Sir, we have so much courage,
no challenge can confront us

1053
01:24:41,477 --> 01:24:43,665
Is it?
- Did I speak too much?

1054
01:24:43,745 --> 01:24:48,767
We will not only restart your resort,
but get it repaired by the one...

1055
01:24:48,847 --> 01:24:50,604
who damaged it

1056
01:24:51,842 --> 01:24:54,882
Did you hear that?
- They are going to die!

1057
01:24:55,515 --> 01:24:58,842
If that happens,
you can meet our daughters

1058
01:25:01,371 --> 01:25:04,313
What have you done!
- We have to jump in the fray now

1059
01:25:04,598 --> 01:25:07,242
Father-in-law, make arrangements
for the marriage

1060
01:25:12,884 --> 01:25:16,004
Peter, two very rich guests
have come to our hotel today

1061
01:25:16,084 --> 01:25:18,164
Cook very tasty food for them

1062
01:25:19,525 --> 01:25:21,364
Are you the owner of this hotel?
- Yes.

1063
01:25:21,523 --> 01:25:23,997
This is a very bad hotel.
You loot people

1064
01:25:24,077 --> 01:25:27,644
What nonsense are you talking?
- I'd ordered a tandoori chicken

1065
01:25:27,984 --> 01:25:30,821
You took full money,
but the chicken had only one leg

1066
01:25:30,901 --> 01:25:33,960
So?
- Do chickens have only one leg?

1067
01:25:34,124 --> 01:25:35,324
Look.

1068
01:25:40,482 --> 01:25:41,563
Look

1069
01:25:41,728 --> 01:25:43,928
You should have whistled like that
at the tandoori chicken

1070
01:25:44,008 --> 01:25:46,088
Even she would remove her
other leg. Now get lost!

1071
01:25:47,505 --> 01:25:50,360
Sir, I showed them the entire
hotel, but they want to meet you

1072
01:25:50,533 --> 01:25:51,848
Is it?
Where are they?

1073
01:25:52,868 --> 01:25:57,003
Good.
- Very pretty.

1074
01:25:59,978 --> 01:26:02,487
Your hotel is great

1075
01:26:02,567 --> 01:26:05,739
Our Sultan wants to come
to such a place for a holiday

1076
01:26:05,819 --> 01:26:11,014
Rafiq, tell me, can you make this
hotel available to us for a month?

1077
01:26:11,094 --> 01:26:14,396
What! The entire hotel for a month?
- Yes

1078
01:26:14,560 --> 01:26:18,313
For the Sultan's
20 wives and his slaves

1079
01:26:18,457 --> 01:26:20,817
20 wives!
- He takes them along everywhere

1080
01:26:21,012 --> 01:26:23,257
And he has another 30 in his harem.
- That means, 50!

1081
01:26:23,337 --> 01:26:26,497
He will marry another 10 next year.
- 60!

1082
01:26:26,711 --> 01:26:30,914
Just tell me whether you can
book the hotel for us or not

1083
01:26:30,994 --> 01:26:34,374
Of course I can. The rent
of each room will be 5000

1084
01:26:34,454 --> 01:26:38,896
What nonsense!
We cannot pay you more than $4000

1085
01:26:38,976 --> 01:26:42,217
What!!
I was thinking of Rs 5000

1086
01:26:42,849 --> 01:26:47,155
He's talking of $4000, which is
Rs 200,000 rent per room!

1087
01:26:47,328 --> 01:26:51,064
We give that much
even in Europe and America

1088
01:26:51,144 --> 01:26:54,187
Since you are giving me such a
big contract, even I'll compromise

1089
01:26:54,267 --> 01:26:59,315
Then we will also pay you
an advance $500,000 next Friday

1090
01:26:59,551 --> 01:27:03,351
But we want the hotel's toilets,
lobby, everything in perfect shape

1091
01:27:03,510 --> 01:27:07,005
Don't worry about that.
I'll renovate the entire hotel

1092
01:27:07,085 --> 01:27:13,500
Damn! Whose tomb is that near
the hotel?

1093
01:27:13,580 --> 01:27:18,240
That! That's no tomb,
it's a resort in ruins

1094
01:27:18,447 --> 01:27:21,648
It looks like a graveyard.
The Sultan cannot stay here

1095
01:27:21,728 --> 01:27:26,811
The Sultan wants beautiful
surroundings all around him

1096
01:27:27,027 --> 01:27:29,933
Do you know, one of the Sultan's
wives had a pimple on her face

1097
01:27:30,130 --> 01:27:32,650
He got plastic surgery
done to her entire face

1098
01:27:32,730 --> 01:27:35,010
Rafiq, the contract
stands canceled!

1099
01:27:35,822 --> 01:27:38,250
Hey no! Listen to me!

1100
01:27:38,893 --> 01:27:46,010
I will get that resort repaired.
- You will the it repaired? Why?

1101
01:27:46,176 --> 01:27:50,010
I only had got it damaged.
- You got it damaged?

1102
01:27:50,130 --> 01:27:53,610
No, actually, my elder
brother was involved in it

1103
01:27:53,812 --> 01:27:56,890
Where is that brother of yours?
- He's in jail now

1104
01:27:57,167 --> 01:27:59,410
He slapped the ACP...

1105
01:27:59,822 --> 01:28:04,170
Forget all that. I'll have the resort
in spick span shape within a week

1106
01:28:04,388 --> 01:28:08,410
All right, then we will also
pay you an advance after a week

1107
01:28:08,645 --> 01:28:10,490
Good day!
- Son-of-a-gun!

1108
01:28:11,530 --> 01:28:13,770
Good day!
Right away!

1109
01:28:34,137 --> 01:28:38,417
Great! Wonderful!

1110
01:28:38,497 --> 01:28:40,897
You have done a great job!

1111
01:28:41,129 --> 01:28:45,697
That roof there has
an empty look.

1112
01:28:46,257 --> 01:28:51,817
Fix the glass chandelier
in your hotel over here.

1113
01:28:52,097 --> 01:28:55,617
Then won't my hotel roof look bad?
- Don't worry about that.

1114
01:28:55,977 --> 01:28:59,817
We fit a diamond chandelier
wherever the Sultan stays.

1115
01:29:00,137 --> 01:29:02,537
What! A diamond chandelier?

1116
01:29:03,140 --> 01:29:06,657
First fix the hotel chandelier there.
Do you know the rate of diamonds?

1117
01:29:11,217 --> 01:29:17,081
Even this door doesn't look good.
Put a good show piece here

1118
01:29:17,161 --> 01:29:21,093
I'll have 3-4 show pieces put here.
- Good! You are working so hard.

1119
01:29:21,417 --> 01:29:23,777
The Sultan will
gift you an oil well.

1120
01:29:23,948 --> 01:29:27,097
Oil well!
I'll fry fritters in them.

1121
01:29:27,817 --> 01:29:30,657
And the advance?
- You'll get it on Friday night.

1122
01:29:30,849 --> 01:29:33,137
Let's go, brother.
- Thank you, sir.

1123
01:29:35,433 --> 01:29:37,777
Live in style!

1124
01:29:41,738 --> 01:29:43,458
Excuse me, sir...
- What is it?

1125
01:29:43,925 --> 01:29:46,858
I've done a hotel management
course. I'm looking for a job.

1126
01:29:46,938 --> 01:29:49,618
No vacancy here.
- Sir, I'm a gold medalist.

1127
01:29:50,057 --> 01:29:51,951
And I was a gold smuggler.
So?

1128
01:29:52,730 --> 01:29:55,187
Secretary! Call up my lawyer.

1129
01:29:59,010 --> 01:30:01,970
Secretary! Call up my lawyer.
- Yes, madam.

1130
01:30:02,050 --> 01:30:04,290
Madam, why call a lawyer?

1131
01:30:04,370 --> 01:30:07,450
A conspiracy is being hatched
in this hotel to kill me.

1132
01:30:07,530 --> 01:30:10,001
Glass pieces have
been put in my ice-cream.

1133
01:30:10,081 --> 01:30:13,461
It must be a mistake, madam.
I'll have the ice-cream replaced.

1134
01:30:13,541 --> 01:30:16,669
And we'll provide you a meal,
all for no-charge.

1135
01:30:16,749 --> 01:30:20,742
Is he a manager or a damager?

1136
01:30:21,423 --> 01:30:24,463
I mean, don't mind,
that way, he'll have you ruined.

1137
01:30:25,023 --> 01:30:27,503
He's doing the right thing.
If she sues us...

1138
01:30:27,583 --> 01:30:29,703
...my hotel will have to be sold,
and even my home.

1139
01:30:29,823 --> 01:30:33,903
What right? Don't mind,
but each one has his own style.

1140
01:30:34,183 --> 01:30:38,023
If I was in his place, the Queen would
pay the bill and also leave a tip.

1141
01:30:39,663 --> 01:30:42,903
Is it?
If you are successful...

1142
01:30:43,195 --> 01:30:46,303
I will kick him out
and appoint you as manager.

1143
01:30:46,383 --> 01:30:47,903
Promise?
- Promise!

1144
01:30:51,377 --> 01:30:52,908
Don't do that, please.

1145
01:30:55,424 --> 01:30:57,145
You!
- I know her.

1146
01:30:57,370 --> 01:30:58,944
I'll convince her, you leave.

1147
01:31:02,663 --> 01:31:06,223
What are you doing here?
- The King will follow the Queen.

1148
01:31:06,979 --> 01:31:09,103
Want to call the police?
I'll call them.

1149
01:31:09,410 --> 01:31:11,583
We'll even show them the
pieces of glass in your purse.

1150
01:31:13,093 --> 01:31:15,383
Abadabada?
What language is that?

1151
01:31:17,391 --> 01:31:20,503
Why are you after us?
- Why do you come before me?

1152
01:31:20,955 --> 01:31:25,983
I will let you off if you pay
the bill, give a decent tip...

1153
01:31:26,063 --> 01:31:27,743
...and leave with a smile.

1154
01:31:29,932 --> 01:31:30,943
I will.

1155
01:31:33,789 --> 01:31:36,783
You also leave.
- We'll have to teach him a lesson.

1156
01:31:38,763 --> 01:31:42,126
You are great!
You are wonderful.

1157
01:31:42,484 --> 01:31:44,283
What did you tell them?
- Don't ask me that.

1158
01:31:44,523 --> 01:31:48,043
Sir, whether a king or his subjects,
I treat everyone like that.

1159
01:31:49,091 --> 01:31:51,403
I appoint you manager
of this hotel from today.

1160
01:31:51,483 --> 01:31:52,723
And me?
- Dismissed.

1161
01:31:52,923 --> 01:31:56,283
No sir, I don't want to
render him jobless.

1162
01:31:56,443 --> 01:31:57,923
Give him some other position.

1163
01:31:59,723 --> 01:32:01,203
I appoint you
laundry manager.

1164
01:32:11,378 --> 01:32:14,658
See! They have started this,
ours that will close

1165
01:32:14,738 --> 01:32:17,618
Their hotel started,
which will render us speechless

1166
01:32:17,698 --> 01:32:19,418
We have even lost that

1167
01:32:19,568 --> 01:32:21,618
What?
- The girls!

1168
01:32:23,036 --> 01:32:26,138
Father-in-law, we did it.
Remember your deal?

1169
01:32:26,418 --> 01:32:27,378
Deal?

1170
01:32:27,458 --> 01:32:31,218
We can meet your
daughters now, can't we?

1171
01:32:31,571 --> 01:32:36,338
You know where you have
to send Sundri and Mundri?

1172
01:32:36,418 --> 01:32:37,410
Where?

1173
01:33:08,787 --> 01:33:11,104
"What are you doing?"

1174
01:33:12,385 --> 01:33:14,664
"I am loving you"

1175
01:33:15,723 --> 01:33:18,144
"But why?"

1176
01:33:19,442 --> 01:33:21,482
"Because my heart says so"

1177
01:33:23,002 --> 01:33:26,642
"Ask your heart to wait
at least until we are married"

1178
01:33:26,722 --> 01:33:29,962
"My heart doesn't listen,
it's revolting"

1179
01:33:30,042 --> 01:33:32,322
"What are you doing?"

1180
01:33:33,482 --> 01:33:35,842
"I'm going home"

1181
01:33:37,002 --> 01:33:39,282
"But why?"

1182
01:33:40,242 --> 01:33:42,722
"Because I'm getting late"

1183
01:33:44,242 --> 01:33:48,122
"Ask your heart,
at least wait until evening"

